{"type": "article", "id": 23105, "title": "剪影挂钩", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-02T07:30:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 60, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702135456Pm1zOgiR7XCwcHSo.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是以色列工作室 artori 推出的挂钩系列，采用剪影的方式，勾画出黑猫和舞女两种图案。黑猫是专门挂在桌边的，有多种形态，比如将头、身体和手都越过了桌面而伸展到桌下，形成了挂钩。舞女则一手高扬挥动扇子，仿佛弗拉明戈舞者，下面悬挂的帕子可以让“她”变得摇曳多姿。这两款挂钩都非常生动，售价 14.9 美元，<a href=\"http://www.artoridesign.com/\">这里是购买链接</a>。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135453Wu9K45sQnIRP1z8d.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.60769231\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135454Ie6ZMP2zQrpt04an.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.39853301\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135454mMjiO9nSyTBzgN6R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.19315403\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135455Zs2TG70UytLuvXiS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.57212714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135455wokBqW1SncEjvsOI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.54645477\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}